p.span: Abilify Maintena 300 mg powder and solvent for prolonged-release suspension for injection in prefilled syringe
Each prefilled syringe contains 300 mg aripiprazole.
After reconstitution each ml of suspension contains 200 mg aripiprazole.
Carmellose sodium, mannitol, sodium dihydrogen phosphate monohydrate, sodium hydroxide
Powder and solvent for prolonged-release suspension for injection
prefilled syringe containing powder in the front chamber and solvent in the rear chamber.
Read the package leaflet before use.
Vertically shake the syringe vigorously for 20 seconds until medicine is uniformly milky-white and use immediately.

title.value: 6. SPECIAL WARNING THAT THE MEDICINAL PRODUCT MUST BE STORED OUT OF THE SIGHT AND REACH OF CHILDREN

p.span: Keep out of the sight and reach of children.

If the injection is not performed immediately after reconstitution, the syringe can be kept below 25 C for up to 2 hours. Shake the syringe vigorously for at least 20 seconds to resuspend prior to injection if the syringe has been left for more than 15 minutes.
Keep the prefilled syringe in the outer carton in order to protect from light.
